      "span_text": "Although a previous study reported an absence of Rac3 expression in the cerebellum [CITATION_2] , our results suggested that both Rac1 and Rac3 are expressed in the developing CGNs and that Rac1 expression is more dominant than that of Rac3 (Fig. S1B )."
